1956;;The Women of Pitcairn Island;;American;;Jean Yarbrough;;Lynn Bari, Sue England;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Women_of_Pitcairn_Island;;Nearly twenty years after the Bounty mutineers landed on Pitcairn Island, the last survivor has died leaving only their local-born widows and children. Tensions arise on the island when a fresh load of shipwrecked sailors arrive.